snippet.title: Minecraft Antichamber?
snippet.description:
This Minecraft map has been inspired by:
- The game Antichamber by Demruth
- Minecraft map Antichamber by Bassintag551
- Minecraft map the Code III by Jesper the End

This is a Minecraft map I started working on a few days ago in the new Minecraft version 1.14. I don't expect this map to be completed any time soon as it's not going to be a small map. In this video you can see a small part of the map whether it's the start or the end or something in the middle, I don't even know myself.

I might start posting some updates on my Twitter:
https://twitter.com/MrKacafirekCZ

-----------------------------------
UPDATE:
Map is finished and it's out on Minecraft Maps.
Download: http://www.minecraftmaps.com/puzzle-maps/antichamber

ANOTHER UPDATE:
I apologize for the bugged map. The map should be updated anytime soon on Minecraft Maps website and it has instructions on how to not lose too much of a progress.
http://www.minecraftmaps.com/puzzle-maps/antichamber
